 Montana - Missoula Recording</td></tr> \r\n<tr><td>Secretary	</td>	<td>Laurie Henneman</td></tr>\r\n<tr><td></td><td>University Of Montana -Dillon</td></tr>\r\n<tr><td>Treasurer	</td>	<td>Tom Lewis</td></tr>\r\n<tr><td></td><td>Montana State University - Billings</td></tr>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n', '<p align="center">Design and Layout ~ <strong>Media Works, Bozeman, Montana</strong></p>\r\n<p align="center">Printing ~ <strong>Bozeman Printing Company, Bozeman, Montana</strong></p>\r\n', NULL, 'Scientific journal', 'Academic Journal', 'Academic Journal', 'The Wildlife Society', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-09-24 15:55:30', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL);
